#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.72"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.2"
msgid "7. Migajālavagga "
msgstr "7. With Migajāla "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.72:0.3"
msgid "72. Dutiyachaphassāyatanasutta "
msgstr "72. Six Fields of Contact (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.44, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.72:1.1"
msgid "“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, anyone who doesn’t truly understand the six fields of contacts’ origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape "

msgctxt "sn35.72:1.2"
msgid "Avusitaṃ tena brahmacariyaṃ, ārakā so imasmā dhammavinayā”ti. "
msgstr "has not completed the spiritual journey and is far from this teaching and training.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.72:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn35.72:2.2"
msgid "“etthāhaṃ, bhante, anassasaṃ panassasaṃ. "
msgstr "“Here, sir, I’m lost, truly lost. "

msgctxt "sn35.72:2.3"
msgid "Ahañhi, bhante, channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "For I don’t truly understand the six fields of contacts’ origin, ending, gratification, drawback, and escape.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn35.72:3.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, bhikkhu, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicant? "

msgctxt "sn35.72:3.2"
msgid "cakkhuṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti? "
msgstr "Do you regard the eye like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn35.72:4.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn35.72:5.1"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, cakkhu ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "“Good, mendicant! And regarding the eye, you will truly see clearly with right wisdom that: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn35.72:5.2"
msgid "Evaṃ te etaṃ paṭhamaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ apunabbhavāya … pe …. "
msgstr "In this way you will give up the first field of contact, so that there are no more future lives. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn35.72:6.1"
msgid "“Jivhaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti? "
msgstr "Do you regard the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn35.72:7.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn35.72:8.1"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, jivhā ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati. Evaṃ te etaṃ catutthaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ apunabbhavāya … pe …. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn35.72:9.1"
msgid "“Manaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassasī”ti? "
msgstr "Do you regard the mind like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn35.72:10.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn35.72:11.1"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhu, ettha ca te, bhikkhu, mano ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya sudiṭṭhaṃ bhavissati. "
msgstr "“Good, mendicant! And regarding the mind, you will truly see clearly with right wisdom that: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn35.72:11.2"
msgid "Evaṃ te etaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ phassāyatanaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati āyatiṃ apunabbhavāyā”ti. "
msgstr "In this way you will give up the sixth field of contact, so that there are no more future lives.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.72:11.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

